text: Kundi may refer to: * Kundi (film), Urdu film from Pakistan * Kundi (harp) * Kundi (Pashtun tribe), in Pakistan * Kundi (stealing power), the practice of stealing electric power in some parts of India * Kundi, Ethiopia, a town in Guradamole, Somali * Kundi, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan * An Assyrian fortress probably identical with later Cyinda
title: Kundi
